{
  "title": "无理数",
  "keywords": "数学,学习,无理数",
  "description": "无理数的概念",
  "author": "",
  "createtime": "",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "title",
      "content": "无理数"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "center",
      "content": "一个 <b>无理数</b> 是一个实数，它 <b>不能</b> 被写为两个整数的比."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "center",
      "class": "large",
      "content": " 无理数和有理数<b>是一对冤家</b>"
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "无理数 pk 有理数"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "class": "center",
      "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/rational-vs-irrational.svg\" alt=\"无理数 pk 有理数\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "threeheading",
      "content": "有理数\t\t\t"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": " 一个<b><a href=\"rational-numbers.html\">有理数</a></b>  <b>可以</b>可以写作<b>两个整数的比</b>."
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "class": "example",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "比如: <b>1.5</b> 是有理数, 因为它可以用 <b>3/2</b>来表示"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "class": "example",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "比如: <b>7</b> 是有理数, 因为它可以表示为 <b>7/1</b>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "class": "example",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "比如: <b>0.333...</b> (3 是无限循环) 也是一个有理数, 因为它可以写作 <b>1/3</b>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "&#xA0;"
    },
    {
      "type": "threeheading",
      "content": "无理数"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "这里总会有一些数 <b>不能</b> 用两个整数之比来表示 ... "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "align": "center",
      "class": "larger",
      "content": "...我们把这些数称为 <b>无理数</b>."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "&#xA0;"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "class": "example",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "例如: <span class=\"times\"><b>&#x3C0;</b> </span><b><a href=\"pi.html\">(Pi)</a></b> 是一个众所周知的无理数. "
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "class": "example2",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "table",
              "border": "0",
              "content": [
                [
                  {
                    "type": "TD",
                    "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/pi1.png\" alt=\"Pi\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "TD",
                    "content": "<p align=\"center\"><b><span class=\"times\"><b>&#x3C0;</b></span> = 3.14159265358979323846264338 (等等等等...)</b></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>我们 <b>不能</b> 用任何两个整数之比来表示 Pi. </p>"
                  }
                ]
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "一个非常大家都认可的近似值是 <span class=\"frac\"><sup>22</sup>/<sub>7</sub></span> = 3.1428571428571... 非常接近 <b>但不是完全一致</b>."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "我们也可以称它们为无限不循环小数.<br>\n\t\t\t"
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "不能用分数来表示"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "我们经常用能不能用分数来表示作为我们判断这个数是有理数或者无理数的依据."
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "class": "example",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "threeheading",
          "content": "比如: <b>4.5</b> 可以用下面的分数来表示:"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "align": "center",
          "class": "larger",
          "content": "4.5 = <span class=\"frac\"><sup>9</sup>/<sub>2</sub></span>"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "align": "center",
          "class": "larger",
          "content": "所以,4.5是一个 <b>有理数</b>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "更多的例子:"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "border": "0",
      "width": "400",
      "align": "center",
      "content": [
        [
          {
            "type": "TH",
            "content": "数字"
          },
          {
            "type": "TH",
            "content": "分数"
          },
          {
            "type": "TH",
            "content": "有理数 或<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t无理数?"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "1.5"
          },
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "3/2"
          },
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "有理数"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "0.001"
          },
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "1/1000"
          },
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "有理数"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "&#x221A;2 <br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t(根号 2)"
          },
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "无法用分数表示"
          },
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "<b>无理数 !</b>"
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "class": "simple",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "subheading",
          "content": "根号 2"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "让我们来仔细看看根号 2."
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "border": "0",
          "align": "center",
          "content": [
            [
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/square-root-2.gif\" alt=\"square root 2\" width=\"102\" height=\"115\">"
              },
              {
                "type": "TD",
                "content": "如果我们画了一个边长为&quot;1&quot;的正方形 , <br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t那它的对角线的长度是多少呢?"
              }
            ]
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": "答案就是 <b><a href=\"square-root.html\">根号</a>  2</b>, 大概是<b> 1.414213562373...(等等等等)</b>"
        },
        {
          "type": "example",
          "class": "indent50px",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": "... 我们 <b>不能用</b> 两个整数的比来表示根号2"
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": "... 这里有详细的 <a href=\"irrational-finding.html\">解释 </a> ,"
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": "... 我们知道它是 <b>一个无理数</b>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "一些大家都知道的无理数"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "border": "0",
      "width": "80%",
      "align": "center",
      "content": [
        [
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/pi1.png\" alt=\"Pi\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">"
          },
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "<p><b><a href=\"pi.html\">Pi</a></b> 是一个大家经常用到的无理数. 是精确计算圆周长、圆面积、球体积等几何形状的关键值. 是一个常数，是代表圆周长和直径的比值:</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>3.1415926535897932384 (等等等等 ...)</p>"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/e1.png\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"e (eulers number)\">"
          },
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "<p> <i><b>e</b></i> (<a href=\"e-eulers-number.html\">欧拉数</a>) 是另一个经常用道的无理数. 它经常在公式中做对数的底.比如,对指数函数和对数函数求导时,就要使用自然常数.可以表示为 :</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>2.718281828459045235  (等等等等 ...)</p>"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/phi.gif\" alt=\"phi\" width=\"97\" height=\"121\">"
          },
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "<p>The <a href=\"golden-ratio.html\">黄金分割</a> 是一个很神秘的无理数.  通常用希腊字母Ф表示这个值,近似值为:</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>1.618033988749... (等等 ...)</p>"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "<img src=\"../public/images/square-root.png\" alt=\"radical symbol\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">"
          },
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "<p>许多平方根, 立方根, 的值都是无理数. 例如:</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"simple\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table border=\"0\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&#x221A;3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1.73205080756887729352 (等等)</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>&#x221A;13</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3.605551275464 (等等)</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>"
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "type": "TD",
            "content": "<p>不过 &#x221A;4 = 2 (有理数), 还有 &#x221A;9 = 3 (有理数) ...</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">... 所以<b>不是所有的</b> 开根号是无理数.</p>"
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "&#xA0;"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "&#xA0;"
    }
  ]
}